  "description": "EXPLORE THE MUSIC PACKS\n\nОб игреA FREESTYLE-DANCE RHYTHM GAME\n\nLet the music move you as you catch notes, ride the rails, and dodge obstacles in a unique combination of freestyle dancing and fitness workout that’ll allow you to burn calories while having tons of fun at the same time.\n\nCUSTOM SONGS officially supported - create your own beatmaps using the free editor today!\n\nBURN CALORIES in a unique combination of freestyle dance & fitness!\n\nMUSIC FOR EVERYONE with over 80 free songs and 127 optional paid DLC tracks feat. Linkin Park, Lady Gaga, Gorillaz, Bruno Mars, Queen, Dua Lipa, and more... \n\n• Meet 10 friends in cross-platform Multiplayer\n\n• Play your way with huge variety of gameplay modifiers & styles including Spin & Spiral\n\n• Incredibly customizable player experience with many great features out of the box including \"custom songs\"",
